{"id":236838,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-62位上海访民在北京祝福被囚禁的冯正虎生/","date":"2012-07-02T16:16:04Z","modified":"2012-07-02T16:16:04Z","title":"维权网 | 62位上海访民在北京祝福被囚禁的冯正虎生日（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-_bb_Qz4bfII/T_HFBrt67nI/AAAAAAAAI5M/dlWX4aCfDsM/s1600/%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%AC%E7%BB%B4%E6%9D%83%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E7%A5%9D%E5%86%AF%E6%AD%A3%E8%99%8E%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%AB%E4%B9%90.JPG\"></a><br /><img border=\"0\" height=\"131\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-_bb_Qz4bfII/T_HFBrt67nI/AAAAAAAAI5M/dlWX4aCfDsM/s320/%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%AC%E7%BB%B4%E6%9D%83%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E7%A5%9D%E5%86%AF%E6%AD%A3%E8%99%8E%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%AB%E4%B9%90.JPG\" width=\"320\" /> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7月1日上海访民在北京为冯正虎送上生日祝福</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-cG4XQiFCJlk/T_HFDJpGjjI/AAAAAAAAI5U/n2nk7pwLuA0/s1600/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E8%BF%9B%E4%BA%AC%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%9A%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%8B%E9%99%85%E6%8F%90%E8%AF%89%E6%B1%82%E6%8A%97%E8%AE%AE.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"131\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-cG4XQiFCJlk/T_HFDJpGjjI/AAAAAAAAI5U/n2nk7pwLuA0/s320/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E8%BF%9B%E4%BA%AC%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%9A%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%8B%E9%99%85%E6%8F%90%E8%AF%89%E6%B1%82%E6%8A%97%E8%AE%AE.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7月1日上海访民在北京要求立案</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>  </span><span>  </span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span>(</span><span>维权网信息员方芳、关小令报道</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)7<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span></span>1<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">日</span></span></span><span>，是上海著名的维权人士冯正虎先生</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">59</span><span>岁生日，上海</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">62</span><span>位正在北京上访的访民因来不及赶回上海，只好在北京为冯正虎先生举办了一场别开生面的生日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Happy</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>   </span></span></div>\n<div><span>自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日起</span><span>，冯正虎先生已经被囚禁在家中</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>个多月了，每天</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>名警察和保安轮流驻守在位于上海市政通路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">240</span><span>号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>号门的冯正虎家楼道内和周围，没有任何手续，冯正虎的家变成了不受法律监督的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>黑监狱</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>    </span></span></div>\n<div><span>近几年，由于上海政府及其有关职能部门不作为、乱作为、违法行政、司法腐败等违法侵权行为的泛滥，造成大量的访民，有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1500</span><span>多名访民常年奔波在上海和北京的有关部门不断上访反映问题。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>     </span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">62</span><span>位正在北京上访的访民听说当天是冯正虎先生的生日，大家相约聚集在北京南站附近一家名为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>东北人家常菜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>的餐馆内，有人买来蛋糕，点了蜡烛，大家欢聚一堂，拉出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>维权公民为冯正虎祈福”、“生日快乐！”、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>还冯正虎自由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>等横幅，大家齐唱生日歌，高呼</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>我要立案、捍卫法律、还我诉权</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>等口号，为冯正虎先生举办了一场别开生面的生日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Happy</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>这场别开生面的生日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Happy</span><span>，吸引了在此就餐的很多客人，很多人表示知道冯正虎的事迹，一位素不相识的北京市民走到上海访民面前，送上了一瓶啤酒与一盆糖拌番茄，（预表甜甜蜜蜜，红红火火），以表示对冯正虎的敬意，他说：他知道冯正虎，很敬佩冯正虎，今天能与上海市民一起庆祝冯正虎生日，感到很荣幸，祝冯正虎先生生日快乐，好人一生平安！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参加冯正虎生日聚餐的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">62</span><span>位访民是：谈兰英、王扣玛、陈国贵、郑培培、朱金娣、徐玮、石萍、贺志勇、袁春生、丁菊英、郎兆刚、田宝成、于义明、朱萍萍、宋龙涛、沈兰珍、严燕文、郭益贵、赵琴珍、汪家荣、黄秀琴、陆杰、周妙如、徐承福、李卫青、郑建明、、陈美芳、冯国伟、俞志欢、李俊、李天红、宋萍珍、王惠明、袁国平、王广山、陈兰珍、全家秋、李自海、张寿珍、沈定高、顾中妹、项惠兰、宋家裕、王翠凤、阮萍、高兰花、张瑜、李玉芳、费爱众、王永凤、谢金花、黄怡芳、申琴芳、周菊仙、金妹珍、周炎、唐建中、卫佩芳、王佩云等，大家强烈谴责上海当局迫害冯正虎的违法犯罪行为，呼吁当局立即释放冯正虎，还冯正虎自由！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-1409934551490426805?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/5df430e2ABE4B990.JPG-150x132.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,17850,20534],"tags":[16910,28519]}